Known bugs for the Freevo project
---------------------------------

o The osd_x11 server doesn't redraw automatically when moving other windows over it.
o The EPG (electronic program guide = TV programs) has misaligned columns.
o The menu headings are not centered.
o The EPG should be reloaded automatically to allow program end/start
o Remote command events cannot be handled fast enough, e.g. when scrolling
  through menu items.
